Homepage: https://github.com/OpenSource-For-Freedom/HARDN-XDR
Description: Linux Security Hardening Extended Detection and Response
 HARDN is a comprehensive Linux security hardening and endpoint defense toolkit.
 It integrates auditing tools, antivirus scanners, system integrity checkers, and
 provides compliance with STIG security guidelines.
 .
 Features:
  - Automated system hardening
  - Log management and monitoring
  - System file integrity checking
  - Intrusion detection and malware scanning
  - Integration with systemd and secure defaults
 .
 Suitable for Debian-based servers, desktops, and headless endpoints in high-security environments.
